ection\">\n<div class=\"text \">\n<p>Looking for Windows software? Try our <a href=\"/about/school-facilities/csil/windows/software.html\">Windows Course Software page</a></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text ruled alternate\">\n<p>The following is a list of Linux based software available in CSIL.</p>\n<p>If you want to get extra software installed, please contact your instructor.</p>\n<h2>Commonly used software</h2>\n<table cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"95%\">\n<tbody><tr><td>Name</td>\n<td>Version</td>\n<td>Availability</td>\n<td>Command</td>\n<td>Reference</td>\n</tr><tr><td>Acroread</td>\n<td>9.4.2</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/acroread</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/\">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr><tr><td>SSH Server</td>\n<td>5.8p1</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/sbin/sshd</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/\">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr><tr><td>SSH Client</td>\n<td>5.8p1</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/ssh</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/\">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr><tr><td>HTML to Text converter</td>\n<td>1.3.2a</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/html2text</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/\">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr><tr><td>Mozilla Firefox</td>\n<td>6.0.1</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/firefox</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/\">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr><tr><td>Postscript to PDF converter</td>\n<td>9.01</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/ps2pdf</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/\">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr><tr><td>Lynx text mode browser</td>\n<td>2.8.8</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/lynx</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/\">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</