ww.eclipse.org/downloads/\">http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/</a></td>\n</tr><tr><td>SWI-Prolog</td>\n<td>5.8.0</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/swipl</td>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.swi-prolog.org/\">http://www.swi-prolog.org</a></td>\n</tr><tr><td>TCL interpreter</td>\n<td>8.4</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/tclsh</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/\">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr><tr></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2>Graphics image processing/tools</h2>\n<table cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"95%\">\n<tbody><tr><td>Name</td>\n<td>Version</td>\n<td>Availability</td>\n<td>Command</td>\n<td>Reference</td>\n</tr><tr><td>Graphics manipulation programs</td>\n<td>10.0</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>all the commands with netpbm packages in /usr/bin</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/\">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr><tr><td>GTK based format image viewer</td>\n<td>1.0.7</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/gqview</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/\">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr><tr><td>Radiance</td>\n<td>4R0</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/radiance</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/\">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr><tr><td>Povray</td>\n<td>3.6.1</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/povray</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/\">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr><tr><td>TK graphical user interface tool kit</td>\n<td>8.4</td>\n<td>CSIL graphics Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/wish</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/\">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr><tr><td>Cinelerra video capturing/editing</td>\n<td>2.1</td>\n<td>CSIL graphics Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/local/bin/cinelerra</td>\n<td><a href=\"http://heroinewarrior.com/\">http://heroinewarrior.com</a></td>\n</tr><tr><td>VTK image processing/visualization</td>\n<td>5.4.2</td>\n<td>CSIL graphics Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/local/bin/vtk</td>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.vtk.org/\">http://www.vtk.org</a></td>\n</tr><tr><td>Blender Animation</td>\n<td>2.49.2</td>\n<td>CSIL graphics Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/blender</td>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.blender.org/\">http://www.blender.org</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text \">\n<p>Verified @ 2012.05.01<br>\n</br></p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"sub_content_wrapper\">\n<div class=\"parsys aboveSubContent\"><div class=\"parbase section reference\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"searchwidget\">\n<div class=\"\">\n<p>Search Computing Science</p>\n<form action=\"/search.html\" method=\"get\">\n<input name=\"q\" placeholder=\"\"/>\n<input class=\"submit\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Search\"/>\n</form>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"parsys sub_content\"><div class=\"parbase section reference\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"text parbase\">\n<div class=\"text relatedTopics\">\n<h3>Course Central<br>\n<br>\n</br></br></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/undergraduate/course-central/course-schedules.html\">Course Schedules</a><br>\n</br></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://portal.cs.sfu.ca/outlines/\">Course Outlines</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/undergraduate/course-central/course-home-page-index-and-maillists.html\">Course Home Page Index and Maillists</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.cs.sfu.ca/about/school-facilities/csil.html\">Computing Science Instruction Labs (CSIL)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/about/school-facilities/csil/windows/software.html\">Course Software (Windows)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/about/school-facilities/csil/unix/software.html\">Course Software (Linux)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.sfu.ca/policies.html\">Grading and Exam Policies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.cs.sfu.ca/CC/tabooking/\">TA Booking and Office Hours</a><br>\n</br></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div