ontentBelow\"><div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text \">\n<p>Â  FOLLOW AND SHARE</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/FAS.SFU\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/content/dam/sfu/images/icons/facebook_32.png\"/></a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/FAS_SFU\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/content/dam/sfu/images/icons/twitter_32.png\"/></a> <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/fas_sfu\" target=\"_blank\"><img height=\"35\" src=\"/content/dam/sfu/images/icons/flickr.png\" width=\"35\"/></a> <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/fascomms\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/content/dam/sfu/images/icons/youtube-icon_32x32.png\"/></a></p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"content_2col\">\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n<a href=\"/computing.html\">Computing Science</a>Â &gt;Â <a href=\"/people.html\">People</a>Â &gt;Â <a href=\"/people/faculty.html\">Faculty</a>Â &gt;Â <a href=\"/people/faculty/arthurliestman.html\">Arthur L. Liestman</a></div>\n<div id=\"main_content_wrapper\">\n<div class=\"parsys main_content\"><div class=\"parsys_column cq-colctrl-lt0 \"><div class=\"parsys_column cq-colctrl-lt0-c0\"><div class=\"title section\"><div><h1>Arthur L. Liestman</h1></div></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text \">\n<p>Professor, School of Computing Science</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text \">\n<h2>Education</h2>\n<p>Ph.D., Computer Science, University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign, United States, 1981</p>\n<p>M.Sc., Computer Science, University of Illinois at Urbana-Chanpaign, United States, 1978<br>\n</br></p>\n<p>B.G.S., Computer Science and Mathematics, University of Kansas, United States, 1975</p>\n<p>Â </p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text listed\">\n<h2>Research interests</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Network structure<br>\n</br></li>\n<li>Network communications<br>\n</br></li>\n<li>Graph theoryÂ Â  Â <br>\n</br></li>\n<li>Graph algorithms</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text listed\">\n<h2>Teaching interests</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Algorithms</li>\n<li>Complexity</li>\n<li>Discrete mathematics</li>\n<li>Technical writing</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"parsys_column cq-colctrl-lt0-c1\"><div class=\"parbase image section\"><img alt=\"Arthur Liestman\" class=\"framed\" src=\"/content/sfu/computing/people/faculty/arthurliestman/_jcr_content/main_content/image.img.jpg/1313520413113.jpg\" title=\"Arthur Liestman\"><br/></img></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text listed\">\n<h2>Contact:</h2>\n<table cellpadding=\"2\">\n<tbody><tr><td>Tel:<br>\n</br></td>\n<td>778.782.4197</td>\n</tr><tr><td>Email:<br>\n</br></td>\n<td><a href=\"mailto:art@cs.sfu.ca\" target=\"_blank\">art@cs.sfu.ca</a></td>\n</tr><tr><td>Fax:<br>\n</br></td>\n<td>778.782.3045Â Â </td>\n</tr><tr><td>Office:<br>\n</br></td>\n<td>SFU Burnaby, TASC 8019</td>\n</tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\">Personal webpage:Â  <a href=\"http://www.cs.sfu.ca/~art/\" target=\"_blank\">www.cs.sfu.ca/~art/</a>Â  Â <br>\n</br></td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</div></div>\n</div></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text listed\">\n<h2>Recently taught courses</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>CMPT 307 Data Structures and Algorithms<br>\n</br></li>\n<li>CMPT 376W Technical Writing and Group Dynamics<br>\n</br></li>\n<li>CMPT 705 Design and Analysis of Algorithms<br>\n</br></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text listed\">\n<h2>Selected recent publications</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>H. A. Harutyunyan, A. L. Liestman, K. Makino, and T. C. Shermer, Non-adaptive Broadcasting in Trees, Networks, to appear.<br>\n</br></li>\n<li>H. A. Harutyunyan, P. Hell, and A. L. Liestman, Messy Broadcasting - Decentralized broadcast schemes with limited knowledge, Discr. Appl. Math. 159: 322-327, 2011.</li>\n<li>A. L. Liestman, T. C. Shermer, and L. Stacho, Edge-Disjoint Spanners in Tori, Discrete Mathematics 309: 2239-2249, 2009.<br>\n</br></li>\n<li>A. L. Liestman, D. Richards, and L. Stacho, Broadcasting from Multiple Originators, Discrete Applied Mathematics157: 2886-2891, 2009.</li>\n<li>H. A. Harutyunyan and A. L. Liestman, A Linear Algorithm for Finding the k-Broadcast Center of a Tree, Networks 53: 287-292, 2008.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br>\nFor more information visit <a href=\"http://www.cs.sfu.ca/~art/publications.html\">www.cs.sfu.ca/~art/publications.html</a>.</br></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/indices/a-tree/l/Liestman:Arthur_L=.html\">Listing</a> on the DBLP CS Bibliography Server.</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"sub_content_wrapper\">\n<div class=\"parsys aboveSubContent\"><div class=\"parbase section reference\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"searchwidget\">\n<div class=\"\">\n<p>Search Computing Science</p>\n<form action=\"/search.html\" method=\"get\">\n<input name=\"q\" placeholder=\"\"/>\n<input class=\"submit\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Search\"/>\n</form>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"parsys sub_content\"><div class=\"parbase section reference\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"text parbase\">\n<div class=\"text \">\n<h2><a href=\"http://www.fas.sfu.ca\">Visit Faculty of Applied Sciences</a><br>\n</br></h2>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"footer\">\n<ul>\n<li>8888 University Drive, Burnaby, B.C. Canada V5A 1S6</li>\n<li><a href=\"//www.sfu.ca/webmaster/terms.html\">Terms / Privacy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"//www.sfu.ca/contact/index.html\">Contact SFU</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"//www.sfu.ca/about/sitemap.html\">SiteMap</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"//www.sfu.ca/security/sfuroadconditions/\">Road Conditions</a></li>\n<li>Â© Simon Fraser University</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<style type=\"text/css\">#banner a { background-image: url(\"/content/sfu/computing/siteconfig/jcr:content/main_content/bannerconfig/leftImage.img.png/1311