arsys_column cq-colctrl-lt0-c0\"><div class=\"title section\"><div><h1>Gabor Tardos</h1></div></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text \">\n<p>Professor, School of Computing Science</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text \">\n<h2>Education</h2>\n<p>Ph.D. Mathematics, Eotvos University, Hungary, 1988<br>\nDiploma in Mathematics, Eotvos University, Hungary, 1987</br></p>\n<p>Â </p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text listed\">\n<h2>Research interests</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Combinatorics</li>\n<li>Discrete and computational geometry</li>\n<li>Complexity theory</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text listed\">\n<h2>Teaching interests</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Complexity</li>\n<li>Algorithms</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"parsys_column cq-colctrl-lt0-c1\"><div class=\"parbase image section\"><img alt=\"Gabor Tardos\" class=\"framed\" src=\"/content/sfu/computing/people/faculty/gabortardos/_jcr_content/main_content/image.img.jpg/1313689610628.jpg\" title=\"Gabor Tardos\"><br/></img></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text \">\n<h2>Contact:</h2>\n<table cellpadding=\"2\">\n<tbody><tr><td>Tel:<br>\n</br></td>\n<td>778.782.7198</td>\n</tr><tr><td>Email:<br>\n</br></td>\n<td><a href=\"mailto:tardos@cs.sfu.ca\" target=\"_blank\">tardos@cs.sfu.ca</a></td>\n</tr><tr><td>Fax:<br>\n</br></td>\n<td>778.782.345Â Â </td>\n</tr><tr><td>Office:<br>\n</br></td>\n<td>SFU Burnaby, TASC 8227</td>\n</tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\">Personal webpage:Â  <a href=\"http://www.cs.sfu.ca/~tardos/\" target=\"_blank\">www.cs.sfu.ca/~tardos/</a>Â  Â <br>\n</br></td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</div></div>\n</div></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text listed\">\n<h2>Recently taught courses</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>CMPT 307 Data Structures and Algorithms<br>\n</br></li>\n<li>CMPT 407 - CMPT 710 Computational Complexity â€“ cross-listed <br>\n</br></li>\n<li>CMPT 710 Computational Complexity<br>\n</br></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"text listed\">\n<h2>Selected recent publications</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>J. Pach, G. Tardos, <a href=\"http://www.renyi.hu/%7Etardos/net.pdf\">Tight lower bounds for the size of epsilon-nets</a>, in <i>Proceedings of the 27th Annual Symposium on Computational Geometry</i>, (SoCG 20011).</li>\n<li>H. Johwari, M. Saglam, G. Tardos, <a href=\"http://www.renyi.hu/%7Etardos/hosseinmert.pdf\">Tight bounds for Lp samplers, finding duplicates, and related problems</a>, <i>Proceedings of the 30th Symposium on Principles of Database Systems</i> (PODS 2011).</li>\n<li>R. Moser, G. Tardos, <a href=\"http://www.renyi.hu/%7Etardos/moser.pdf\">A constructive proof of the general LovÃ¡sz Local Lemma</a>, <i>Journal of the ACM</i> <b>57</b> (2010) (2) Art. 11, 15pp.</li>\n<li>E. Amiri, G. Tardos, <a href=\"http://www.renyi.hu/%7Etardos/amiri.pdf\">High rate fingerprinting codes and the fingerprinting capacity</a>, in <i>Proceedings of the 20th Annual ACM-SIAM Symposium on Discrete Algorithms</i> (SODA 2009), 336--345.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br>\nSee comprehensive <a href=\"http://www.renyi.hu/~tardos/publications.html\">publications list.</a></br></p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"sub_content_wrapper\">\n<div class=\"parsys aboveSubContent\"><div class=\"parbase section reference\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"searchwidget\">\n<div class=\"\">\n<p>Search Computing Science</p>\n<form action=\"/search.html\" method=\"get\">\n<input name=\"q\" placeholder=\"\"/>\n<input class=\"submit\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Search\"/>\n</form>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"parsys sub_content\"><div class=\"parbase section reference\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"text parbase\">\n<div class=\"text \">\n<h2><a href=\"http://www.fas.sfu.ca\">Visit Faculty of Applied Sciences</a><br>\n</br