r 2012)<br/>\n            Under a <a href=\"http://www.mitacs.ca/elevate\">MITACS Elevate Postdoc Fellowship </a> at \n    the <a href=\"http://www.cs.sfu.ca\">School of Computing Science</a>,\n            at <a href=\"http://www.sfu.ca\">Simon Fraser University</a>,\n            with the industrial partner <a href=\"http://www.pdftron.com/\">PDFTron Inc.</a>\n            My supervisor at SFU was\n            <a href=\"http://www.cs.sfu.ca/~haoz\">Hao (Richard) Zhang</a>.\n        </li>\n<li>\n            PhD in Computing Science (September 2005 - November 2011)<br/>\n<a href=\"http://www.cs.sfu.ca\">School of Computing Science</a>,\n            <a href=\"http://fas.sfu.ca\">Faculty of Applied Sciences</a>,\n            <a href=\"http://www.sfu.ca\">Simon Fraser University</a>,\n            <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Burnaby\">Burnaby</a>,\n            <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/British_Columbia\">BC</a>, <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Canada\">Canada</a>.<br/>\n            My supervisors were\n            <a href=\"http://www.cs.sfu.ca/~haoz\">Hao (Richard) Zhang</a>\n            and <a href=\"http://www.cs.sfu.ca/~hamarneh/\">Ghassan Hamarneh</a>.<br/>\n            I was affiliated with the <a href=\"http://gruvi.cs.sfu.ca/\">GrUVi Lab</a> and the\n            <a href=\"http://mial.fas.sfu.ca/\">Medical Image Analysis Lab</a>.\n        </li>\n<li>\n            M.Sc. in Computer Science (2003-2005)<br/>\n<a href=\"http://www.inf.ufpr.br\">Computer Science Department</a><br/>\n<a href=\"http://www.ufpr.br\">Federal University of Parana</a>,\n            <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Curitiba\">Curitiba</a>,\n            <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paran%C3%A1_%28state%29\">PR</a>,\n            <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brazil\">Brazil</a><br/>\n            My supervisor was\n            <a href=\"http://www.ic.unicamp.br/~helio/\">HÃ©lio Pedrini</a>.\n        </li>\n<li>\n        B.Sc. in Computer Science (1999-2003)<br/>\n        Computer Science Department<br/>\n        Federal University of Parana, Curitiba, PR, Brazil\n        </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h1>Contact</h1>\n<p>\n<b>E-mail:</b> ovankaic at sfu dot ca<br/>\n<b>Phone:</b> +1 (778) 782-3610 (GrUVi Lab)\n        </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"footer\">\n<p>Last update: Mar 4th, 2013.</p>\n</div>\n</body></html>\n','2013-04-01 08:00:12.699012'),('http://www.cs.sfu.ca/~tamaras/','Tamara Smyth','<!DOCTYPE HTML>\n\n<html>\n<head>\n<title>Tamara Smyth</title>\n<style type=\"text/css\">\nbody {font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\n      font-size:100%;\n      width: 750px;\n      margin: auto}\n\nh1 {background-color: #333333;\n    color: #EAEAEA;\n    height: 40px;\n    font-family: fantasy;\n    font-variant: small-caps;\n    margin-bottom: -15px;\n    padding-top: 5px;\n    padding-bottom: 10px;}\n\n#head {width: 750px;\n       height: 285px;\n       line-height: 130%;}\n\n#title {line-height: 140%;}\n\n#contact {font-size:90%;\n          padding-top: 30px;}\n\n#me {float: right;\n     border: 5px ridge black;}\n\n#nav {background-color: #333333;\n      margin-top: -16px;\n      font-size: 101.5%;}\n\n#nav ul {text-align: right;\n         margin-left:-40px;}\n\n#nav li {display: inline-block;\n         font-family: fantasy;\n         font-variant: small-caps;}\n\n#nav span {display: none;}\n\n#nav a {display: inline-block;\n        padding-left: 17px;\n        padding-right: 17px;\n        padding-top: 15px;\n        padding-bottom: 10px;}\n\n#nav a:link {color: #EAEAEA;}\n#nav a:visited {color: #EAEAEA;}\n#nav a:hover {color: #000066;\n              background-color: #EAEAEA;}\n#nav a:hover span {display: inline-block;\n                   position: absolute;\n                   top: 410px;\n                   left: 400px;}\n\n\n#research li {margin-bottom:10px;}\n#courses li {margin-bottom:10px;}\n#download li {margin-bottom:10px;\n              line-height: 140%; }\n#studentnote {text-align: justify;\n              line-height: 140%; }\n\na {text-decoration: none;}\na:link {color: #000066;}\na:visited {color: #000066;}\na:hover {color: #000066;}\n\ntable {margin: auto;\n       margin-top:20px;\n       width: 700px;\n       border: 1px solid black;}\n\ncaption {font-weight: bold;\n        padding-bottom: 5px;}\ntd {padding: 5px;}\ntr:nth-of-type(even) {background-color:#EAEAEA;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h1>Tamara Smyth</h1>\n<div id=\"head\">\n<img alt=\"Tamara Smyth\" height=\"275px\" id=\"me\" src=\"littleme2.jpg\">\n<p id=\"title\">\nAssistant Professor<br>\n<a href=\"http://www.cs.sfu.ca/\">School of Computing Science</a><br>\n<a href=\"http://www.sfu.ca/\">Simon Fraser University</a><br>\n</br></br></br></p>\n<p id=\"contact\">\nSimon Fraser University Surrey<br>\n250-13450 102nd Ave.<br>\nSurrey, B.C. Canada V3T 0A3<br>\nT 778.782.7585<br>\nF 778.782.8116<br>\ntamaras[at]cs.sfu.ca<br>\n</br></br></br></br></br></br></p>\n</img></div>\n<div id=\"nav\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#research\">Research</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#courses\">Teaching</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"resume/resume.pdf\">CV</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"pubs/Publications.html\">Publications</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#download\">Download</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#studentnote\">Prospective Students</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"research\">\n<h3>Research Interests</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Computer Music</li>\n<li>Musical Acoustics and Measurement Techniques</li>\n<li>Sound Analysis/Synthesis</li>\n<li>Digital Audio Signal Processing</li>\n<li>Acoustic Modelling and Inverse Modelling for Parameter Estimation</li>\n<li>Simulation of Reed-Based Musical Instruments and Acoustic Tubes</li>\n<li>Control of (Virtual) Musical Instruments</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"courses\">\n<h3>Courses</h3>\n<ul>\n<h4>Spring 2012</h4>\n<li><a href=\"intro889/\">CMPT 889: Computational Acoustic\n  Modelling</a>, Spring 2012</li>\n<h4>Past Semesters</h4>\n<li><a href=\"intro165/\">CMPT 165: Introduction to the Internet and\n  the World Wide Web</a>, Fall 2011</li>\n<li><a href=\"intro468/\">CMPT 468/768: Computer Music Theory and\n  Sound Synthesis</a>, Spring 2009, 2010, Fall 2011</li>\n<li><a href=\"intro889/\">CMPT 889: Computational Acoustic\n  Modelling</a>, Fall 2005, 2006, 2007, 2009</li>\n<li><a href=\"intro125\">CMPT 125: Introduction to Computing Science\n  and Programming II</a>, Spring 2009</li>\n<li><a href=\"intro318/\">CMPT 318: Fundamentals of Computerized\n  Sound</a>, Spring 2005, 2006</li>\n<li><a href=\"intro368/\">CMPT 368: Computer Music Theory and Sound\n  Synthesis</a>, Spring 2007, 2008</li>\n<li><a href=\"intro126\">CMPT 126: Introduction to Computing Science\n  and Programming, Fall 2006, 2007</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"download\">\n<h3>Download</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/resume/resume.pdf\">Curriculum Vitae (PDF)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"pubs/Publications.html\">Online Publications</a></li>\n<li>Requested Conference and Presentation Materials (more to come):\n    <ul>\n<li><b>Sound and Music Computing (SMC) 2011, Padova, Italy</b>: <q>Parametric Trombone\n    Synthesis by Coupling Dynamic Lip Valve and Instrument Models</q>, \n    <a href=\"smc11slides.pptx\">Power Point slides (with sound examples)</a></li>\n<li><b>Acoustical Society of America (ASA) Meeting in Hawaii, 28 Nov - 2\n    Dec, 2006</b>: <q>Observing the Effects of Waveguide Model Elements in Acoustic Tube\n    Measurements</q>, presentation slides in \n    <a href=\"asaHonoluluSlides2006.pdf\">PDF</a>, \n    <a href=\"asa.ppt\">Power Point</a>, \n    <a href=\"asa.ppt.htm\">HTML</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<li>Tymbalimba Video Clips:\n  <ul>\n<li><img height=\"55\" src=\"buckle1.jpg\">\n<a href=\"tamara2.mpg\">Tamara plays the Tymbalimba</a></img></li>\n<li><img height=\"55\" src=\"howdoesitwork.jpg\">\n<a href=\"tamara3.mpg\">How does it work?</a></img></li>\n<li><img height=\"55\" src=\"jeffblurr.jpg\">\n<a href=\"jeff.mpg\">Jeff (percussionist) plays the Tymbalimba</a></img></li>\n</ul>\n<li> Syri